    "name": "永恒守望",
    "steam_appid": 2307170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/9be1c4807d168a1066124fde791508c0.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=100 /></span>在《永恒守望》中，存在着你和这个由算法生成的黑暗世界。触碰它吧，它会召唤出一个怪物，试图摧毁你最珍贵的事物——一颗困住你朋友的水晶。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f02b7113ad1f328a6fb9e0a0f1a5e778.poster.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f02b7113ad1f328a6fb9e0a0f1a5e778.webm?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f02b7113ad1f328a6fb9e0a0f1a5e778.mp4?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/5db4b5706ede30aade3c16fca9918d09.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=100 /></span>每次挑战将带着一部分资源开始。后续如何对抗黑暗，完全取决于你。你可以稳扎稳打，逐步扩展领地，清除黑暗，收集能量，谨慎地部署防御者来对抗黑暗中涌现的敌人；或者你也可以大胆冒险，快速出击，寻找隐藏在黑暗中的远古遗迹和强力神器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/9673e40d632ec83548e653c4b4d7048c.poster.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/9673e40d632ec83548e653c4b4d7048c.webm?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/9673e40d632ec83548e653c4b4d7048c.mp4?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/94f7be4fa09ca748ed23954ee9c9c0eb.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=100 /></span>失败不过是学习的另一种形式。每次游玩后，你都会收集到星矿，并解锁科技树上的新选项，使你在对抗黑暗时变得更强，能坚持得更久。毕竟，时间不站在你这一边：随着时间的流逝，敌人会变得越来越强大——但你也会变强，收集新的资源、提升防御者，争取在黑暗中再坚持一会儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/eaf79bad27ab1bd3c544060e1d267921.poster.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/eaf79bad27ab1bd3c544060e1d267921.webm?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/eaf79bad27ab1bd3c544060e1d267921.mp4?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/b589e6ac67b55d7740c0d01a71eb64eb.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次挑战都是随机生成的，带有独特的难关和变化，时刻让你保持警觉。每一次升级都会改变游戏体验，创造出更多协同效果。因此每当你在敌潮压力中苦苦支撑的时候，总有办法扭转胜局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.poster.avif?t=1771357685\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.webm?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307170/extras/f810c7188f796a6997fe29b5dcc753f7.mp4?t=1771357685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
